quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  42,51,Non human est communicate DEUS absque inspiration behind barrier sending messenger per He reveals quod He testimentum. He est the Multus High Wise
  42,52,Sic nos inspired vos revelation proclaiming noster commandments! Vos non habet idea scripture faith. Nos factus hoc beacon guide whomever nos choose noster servus. Surely vos guide straight path
  42,53,path DEUS to whom belongs everything caelum everything terra. Absolutely totus matters controlled DEUS
  43,1,M
  43,2,Ac enlightening scripture
  43,3,Nos rendered it Arabic Quran vos understand
  43,4,It preserved nos in original magister prenobilis foderator de wisdom
  43,5,Nos just ignore vos transgressed limits
  43,6,Nos sent multus prophet proximus generations
  43,7,Omnis temporis prophet iit them they ridiculed eum
  43,8,Consequently nos annihilated people est et powerful than these. Nos ergo set examples ex proximus communities
  43,9,Vos asked them Qui created caelum terra they dictus Almighty Omniscient created them
  43,10,He est Unus factus terra habitable vos created pro vos via therein ut vos subsequentis the statim via
  43,11,He est Unus sends down caelum aqua exact measure revive denatus terra ut! Similarly vos resurrected
  43,12,He est Unus created totus generis in pairs (vir femina) ac He created vos ships livestock ride
  43,13,Prout vos rest them vos appreciate such beatus tuus Dominus dictus Glory est Unus subdued hoc nos! Nos non controlled them ourselves
  43,14,Nos ultimately return noster Dominus
  43,15,They et assigned pro Eum share ex His suus creation! Surely human est est profoundly unappreciative
  43,16,He chosen ex His creations filia Ipse dum beatus vos filius
  43,17,When unus de them dedit news (de filia) prout they claimed the Multus Gracious his face darkened misery anger
  43,18,(They dictus) Quod bonus proles est brought est beautiful help in non war
  43,19,They claimed ut angels est servus the Multus Gracious est femina! they testis their creation? Their claims actum they asked
  43,20,They et dictus the Multus Gracious willed nos non worshipped them. They non habet basis such claim they unus conjecture
  43,21,Nos dedit them book hoc they upholding it
  43,22,fact est ut they dictus Nos invenit noster parentes carrying certain practices nos subsequentis in their footsteps
  43,23,Invariably when nos sent warner any community dux ut community dictus Nos invenit noster parentes posterus certain practices nos continue in their footsteps